{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782445022526,"sessionID":"ses_0fe058cafffeQXWj8wzo54yLAu","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_sRzi95by1p3fjLSs8MbNk7o2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\random\\README.md","offset":1,"limit":220},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\random\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # 仓颉语言随机数 Skill\n2: \n3: ## 1. Random 类\n4: \n5: - 来自 `std.random.*`\n6: - 构造：`Random()` 使用默认种子，`Random(seed: UInt64)` 指定种子\n7: - `seed` 属性：获取当前种子值\n8: \n9: ---\n10: \n11: ## 2. 常用方法\n12: \n13: | 方法 | 说明 |\n14: |------|------|\n15: | `nextBool(): Bool` | 随机布尔值 |\n16: | `nextInt8/16/32/64(): IntN` | 随机有符号整数 |\n17: | `nextUInt8/16/32/64(): UIntN` | 随机无符号整数 |\n18: | `nextFloat16/32/64(): FloatN` | 随机浮点数，范围 [0.0, 1.0) |\n19: | `nextInt64(upper: Int64): Int64` | 随机整数，范围 [0, upper) |\n20: | `nextBytes(length: Int32): Array<Byte>` | 随机字节数组 |\n21: | `nextGaussianFloat64(mean!: Float64, sigma!: Float64): Float64` | 高斯分布随机数 |\n22: \n23: ```cangjie\n24: package test_proj\n25: import std.random.*\n26: \n27: main() {\n28:     let m: Random = Random(3)\n29:     let b: Bool = m.nextBool()\n30:     let c: Int8 = m.nextInt8()\n31:     print(\"b=${b is Bool},\")\n32:     println(\"c=${c is Int8}\")\n33:     return 0\n34: }\n35: ```\n36: \n37: ```cangjie\n38: package test_proj\n39: import std.random.*\n40: \n41: main(): Unit {\n42:     let rng = Random()\n43: \n44:     // 生成范围内的随机整数\n45:     let n = rng.nextInt64(100)\n46:     println(\"随机数 [0, 100): ${n}\")\n47: \n48:     // 生成随机浮点数\n49:     let f = rng.nextFloat64()\n50:     println(\"随机浮点 [0.0, 1.0): ${f}\")\n51: \n52:     // 生成随机字节数组\n53:     let bytes = rng.nextBytes(8)\n54:     println(\"随机字节长度: ${bytes.size}\")\n55: \n56:     // 高斯分布\n57:     let g = rng.nextGaussianFloat64(mean: 0.0, sigma: 1.0)\n58:     println(\"高斯随机数: ${g}\")\n59: }\n60: ```\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## 3. 关键规则速查\n65: \n66: 1. `Random(seed)` 相同种子产生相同序列，适合可复现测试\n67: 2. `Random()` 使用系统默认种子，每次运行结果不同\n68: 3. `nextFloat16/32/64()` 返回 [0.0, 1.0) 左闭右开区间\n69: 4. `nextInt64(upper)` 参数必须大于 0，否则抛异常\n70: 5. `nextGaussianFloat64` 使用命名参数 `mean:` 和 `sigma:`\n71: 6. `Random` 非线程安全，多线程场景应各自创建实例\n\n(End of file - total 71 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# 仓颉语言随机数 Skill\n\n## 1. Random 类\n\n- 来自 `std.random.*`\n- 构造：`Random()` 使用默认种子，`Random(seed: UInt64)` 指定种子\n- `seed` 属性：获取当前种子值\n\n---\n\n## 2. 常用方法\n\n| 方法 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `nextBool(): Bool` | 随机布尔值 |\n| `nextInt8/16/32/64(): IntN` | 随机有符号整数 |\n| `nextUInt8/16/32/64(): UIntN` | 随机无符号整数 |\n| `nextFloat16/32/64(): FloatN` | 随机浮点数，范围 [0.0, 1.0) |\n| `nextInt64(upper: Int64): Int64` | 随机整数，范围 [0, upper) |\n| `nextBytes(length: Int32): Array<Byte>` | 随机字节数组 |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\random\\README.md","time":{"start":1782445022516,"end":1782445022525}},"id":"prt_f02009d03001nCJFzob7GC4wCN","sessionID":"ses_0fe058cafffeQXWj8wzo54yLAu","messageID":"msg_f02005f77001BQaVF6mWA4fC0O"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782445022576,"sessionID":"ses_0fe058cafffeQXWj8wzo54yLAu","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_sS7dQemSS7eZ4BeMAFtVaorn","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\collection\\README.md","offset":1,"limit":260},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\collection\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # 仓颉语言集合数据结构 Skill\n2: \n3: ## 1. 概述\n4: \n5: `std.collection` 包提供丰富的泛型集合数据结构和函数式迭代操作，是仓颉标准库中最常用的包之一。\n6: \n7: **导入**：`import std.collection.*`\n8: \n9: ---\n10: \n11: ## 2. 集合类型\n12: \n13: ### 2.1 ArrayList — 动态数组\n14: \n15: 最常用的线性集合，基于数组实现，支持随机访问和动态扩容。\n16: \n17: | 方法 / 属性 | 说明 |\n18: |-------------|------|\n19: | `ArrayList<T>()` | 创建空列表 |\n20: | `ArrayList<T>(capacity: Int64)` | 指定初始容量 |\n21: | `ArrayList<T>(elements: Collection<T>)` | 从集合构造 |\n22: | `ArrayList<T>(size: Int64, initElement: (Int64) -> T)` | 指定大小和初始化函数 |\n23: | `add(element: T): Unit` | 尾部追加 |\n24: | `add(element: T, at!: Int64): Unit` | 指定位置插入 |\n25: | `get(index: Int64): T` | 按索引读取 |\n26: | `set(index: Int64, element: T): Unit` | 按索引设置 |\n27: | `remove(at!: Int64): T` | 删除指定位置元素 |\n28: | `size: Int64` | 当前元素数量 |\n29: | `isEmpty(): Bool` | 是否为空 |\n30: | `contains(element: T): Bool` | 是否包含（需 T <: Equatable） |\n31: | `operator[](index: Int64)` | 下标访问（读/写） |\n32: | `iterator(): Iterator<T>` | 获取迭代器 |\n33: \n34: ```cangjie\n35: package test_proj\n36: import std.collection.*\n37: \n38: main() {\n39:     let list = ArrayList<String>()\n40:     list.add(\"Alice\")\n41:     list.add(\"Bob\")\n42:     list.add(\"Charlie\")\n43: \n44:     // 下标访问\n45:     println(list[0])  // Alice\n46: \n47:     // 迭代\n48:     for (name in list) {\n49:         print(\"${name} \")\n50:     }\n51:     println(\"\")  // Alice Bob Charlie\n52: \n53:     // 插入和删除\n54:     list.add(\"Dave\", at: 1)   // 在索引1插入\n55:     list.remove(at: 2)        // 删除索引2的元素(Bob)\n56:     println(\"size: ${list.size}\")  // size: 3\n57: \n58:     // 从数组构造\n59:     let nums = ArrayList<Int64>([1, 2, 3, 4, 5])\n60:     println(nums[2])  // 3\n61: }\n62: ```\n63: \n64: ### 2.2 HashMap — 哈希映射\n65: \n66: 基于哈希表的键值映射，要求 `K <: Hashable & Equatable<K>`。\n67: \n68: | 方法 / 属性 | 说明 |\n69: |-------------|------|\n70: | `HashMap<K, V>()` | 创建空映射 |\n71: | `HashMap<K, V>(capacity: Int64)` | 指定初始容量 |\n72: | `HashMap<K, V>(elements: Array<(K, V)>)` | 从键值对数组构造 |\n73: | `add(key: K, value: V): ?V` | 添加或更新，返回旧值 |\n74: | `get(key: K): ?V` | 获取值，不存在返回 None |\n75: | `contains(key: K): Bool` | 判断键是否存在 |\n76: | `remove(key: K): ?V` | 删除键值对，返回旧值 |\n77: | `size: Int64` | 当前元素数量 |\n78: | `operator[](key: K)` | 下标访问（读/写） |\n79: \n80: ```cangjie\n81: package test_proj\n82: import std.collection.*\n83: \n84: main() {\n85:     let map = HashMap<String, Int64>()\n86:     map[\"Alice\"] = 90\n87:     map[\"Bob\"] = 85\n88:     map[\"Charlie\"] = 95\n89: \n90:     // 读取\n91:     println(map[\"Alice\"])  // 90\n92: \n93:     // 安全读取\n94:     match (map.get(\"Dave\")) {\n95:         case Some(score) => println(\"Dave: ${score}\")\n96:         case None => println(\"Dave not found\")\n97:     }\n98: \n99:     // 遍历\n100:     for ((name, score) in map) {\n101:         print(\"${name}=${score} \")\n102:     }\n103:     println(\"\")\n104: \n105:     // 从数组构造\n106:     let m2 = HashMap<String, Int64>([(\"x\", 1), (\"y\", 2)])\n107:     println(\"contains x: ${m2.contains(\"x\")}\")  // true\n108: }\n109: ```\n110: \n111: ### 2.3 HashSet — 哈希集合\n112: \n113: 基于哈希表的集合，要求 `T <: Hashable & Equatable<T>`，元素不重复。\n114: \n115: ```cangjie\n116: package test_proj\n117: import std.collection.*\n118: \n119: main() {\n120:     let set = HashSet<Int64>()\n121:     set.add(1)\n122:     set.add(2)\n123:     set.add(3)\n124:     set.add(2)  // 重复元素不会添加\n125: \n126:     println(\"size: ${set.size}\")  // size: 3\n127:     println(\"contains 2: ${set.contains(2)}\")  // true\n128: \n129:     // 集合运算\n130:     let setA = HashSet<Int64>([1, 2, 3])\n131:     let setB = HashSet<Int64>([2, 3, 4])\n132:     // 遍历\n133:     for (v in setA) {\n134:         print(\"${v} \")\n135:     }\n136:     println(\"\")\n137: }\n138: ```\n139: \n140: ### 2.4 TreeMap — 有序映射\n141: \n142: 基于红黑树的有序映射，要求 `K <: Comparable<K>`，按键有序。\n143: \n144: ```cangjie\n145: package test_proj\n146: import std.collection.*\n147: \n148: main() {\n149:     let tm = TreeMap<String, Int64>([(\"banana\", 2), (\"apple\", 1), (\"cherry\", 3)])\n150: \n151:     // 按键有序遍历\n152:     for ((k, v) in tm) {\n153:         println(\"${k}: ${v}\")\n154:     }\n155:     // 输出: apple: 1, banana: 2, cherry: 3\n156: \n157:     println(\"size: ${tm.size}\")\n158: }\n159: ```\n160: \n161: ### 2.5 TreeSet — 有序集合\n162: \n163: 基于红黑树的有序集合，要求 `T <: Comparable<T>`，元素有序不重复。\n164: \n165: ```cangjie\n166: package test_proj\n167: import std.collection.*\n168: \n169: main() {\n170:     let ts = TreeSet<Int64>([3, 1, 4, 1, 5, 9, 2, 6])\n171: \n172:     // 有序且去重\n173:     for (v in ts) {\n174:         print(\"${v} \")\n175:     }\n176:     println(\"\")  // 1 2 3 4 5 6 9\n177: \n178:     println(\"size: ${ts.size}\")  // 7\n179: }\n180: ```\n181: \n182: ### 2.6 LinkedList — 双向链表\n183: \n184: 双向链表，支持高效的头尾插入删除。核心方法是 `addFirst`/`addLast`/`removeFirst`/`removeLast`，以及基于 `LinkedListNode` 的精确位置操作。\n185: \n186: `addFirst`/`addLast`/`addBefore`/`addAfter` 返回 `LinkedListNode<T>`，可用于后续精确位置插入或删除：\n187: \n188: ```cangjie\n189: package test_proj\n190: import std.collection.*\n191: \n192: main() {\n193:     let ll = LinkedList<String>()\n194:     let nodeA = ll.addLast(\"A\")\n195:     ll.addLast(\"B\")\n196:     ll.addLast(\"C\")\n197: \n198:     // 基于节点的精确位置插入\n199:     ll.addAfter(nodeA, \"X\")    // A 之后插入 X\n200:     for (v in ll) { print(\"${v} \") }\n201:     println(\"\")  // A X B C\n202: \n203:     // 基于节点删除\n204:     ll.remove(nodeA)\n205:     for (v in ll) { print(\"${v} \") }\n206:     println(\"\")  // X B C\n207: \n208:     println(\"size: ${ll.size}\")  // 3\n209: }\n210: ```\n211: \n212: ### 2.7 ArrayDeque / ArrayQueue / ArrayStack\n213: \n214: | 类型 | 接口 | 核心操作 |\n215: |------|------|----------|\n216: | `ArrayDeque<T>` | `Deque<T>` | `addFirst(T)`, `addLast(T)`, `removeFirst(): ?T`, `removeLast(): ?T`, `first: ?T`, `last: ?T` |\n217: | `ArrayQueue<T>` | `Queue<T>` | `add(T)`, `remove(): ?T`, `peek(): ?T` |\n218: | `ArrayStack<T>` | `Stack<T>` | `add(T)`, `remove(): ?T`, `peek(): ?T` |\n219: \n220: ```cangjie\n221: package test_proj\n222: import std.collection.*\n223: \n224: main() {\n225:     // 栈 — 后进先出（add=入栈，remove=出栈，peek=查看栈顶）\n226:     let stack = ArrayStack<Int64>()\n227:     stack.add(1)\n228:     stack.add(2)\n229:     stack.add(3)\n230:     println(\"peek: ${stack.peek()}\")    // Some(3)\n231:     println(\"remove: ${stack.remove()}\")  // Some(3)\n232: \n233:     // 队列 — 先进先出（add=入队，remove=出队，peek=查看队首）\n234:     let queue = ArrayQueue<String>()\n235:     queue.add(\"first\")\n236:     queue.add(\"second\")\n237:     println(\"remove: ${queue.remove()}\")  // Some(first)\n238: \n239:     // 双端队列\n240:     let deque = ArrayDeque<Int64>()\n241:     deque.addFirst(1)\n242:     deque.addLast(2)\n243:     deque.addFirst(0)\n244:     println(\"first: ${deque.first}, last: ${deque.last}\")  // first: Some(0), last: Some(2)\n245: }\n246: ```\n247: \n248: ---\n249: \n250: ## 3. 集合接口\n251: \n252: | 接口 | 关键方法 | 说明 |\n253: |------|----------|------|\n254: | `Collection<T>` | `size`, `isEmpty()`, `toArray()` | 集合基础接口 |\n255: | `List<T>` | `get(Int64)`, `set(Int64, T)`, `add(T)`, `remove(at: Int64)` | 可变列表 |\n256: | `ReadOnlyList<T>` | `get(Int64)`, `size` | 只读列表 |\n257: | `Map<K, V>` | `get(K)`, `add(K, V)`, `contains(K)`, `remove(K)` | 可变映射 |\n258: | `ReadOnlyMap<K, V>` | `get(K)`, `contains(K)`, `size` | 只读映射 |\n259: | `Set<T>` | `add(T)`, `contains(T)`, `remove(T)` | 可变集合 |\n260: | `ReadOnlySet<T>` | `contains(T)`, `size` | 只读集合 |\n\n(Showing lines 1-260 of 386. Use offset=261 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# 仓颉语言集合数据结构 Skill\n\n## 1. 概述\n\n`std.collection` 包提供丰富的泛型集合数据结构和函数式迭代操作，是仓颉标准库中最常用的包之一。\n\n**导入**：`import std.collection.*`\n\n---\n\n## 2. 集合类型\n\n### 2.1 ArrayList — 动态数组\n\n最常用的线性集合，基于数组实现，支持随机访问和动态扩容。\n\n| 方法 / 属性 | 说明 |\n|-------------|------|\n| `ArrayList<T>()` | 创建空列表 |\n| `ArrayList<T>(capacity: Int64)` | 指定初始容量 |","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\collection\\README.md","time":{"start":1782445022570,"end":1782445022576}},"id":"prt_f02009d36001PbaCqzXkCEwzGF","sessionID":"ses_0fe058cafffeQXWj8wzo54yLAu","messageID":"msg_f02005f77001BQaVF6mWA4fC0O"}}
